== org.jawata.jdtpatch (added 2026-07-11, Sprint 22c) ==
Contains a single modified class from Eclipse JDT (org.eclipse.jdt.core.compiler.batch,
Eclipse Public License 2.0, https://www.eclipse.org/legal/epl-2.0/):
org.eclipse.jdt.internal.compiler.problem.ProblemReporter — one null-guard added for
https://github.com/eclipse-jdt/eclipse.jdt.core/issues/5188; shipped as an OSGi patch
fragment and removed when the upstream fix ships. The combined work remains AGPL-3.0 as stated above; this fragment additionally carries its EPL-2.0 notices.
